Rong 
<emphasis box="[1205,1254,1086,1112]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="420">et al</emphasis>
. 2017
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="420" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,870,1184]" pageId="5" pageNumber="420">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,1122,1148]" pageId="5" pageNumber="420">Remarks:</emphasis>
So far, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Wileman" baseAuthorityYear="1911" box="[409,538,1122,1148]" class="Insecta" family="Pyralidae" genus="Termioptycha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="420" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bilineata">
<emphasis box="[409,538,1122,1148]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="420">T. bilineata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is reported from 
<collectingCountry box="[738,805,1122,1148]" name="China" pageId="5" pageNumber="420">China</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[862,929,1123,1149]" name="Japan" pageId="5" pageNumber="420">Japan</collectingCountry>
. Reporting of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Wileman" baseAuthorityYear="1911" box="[1093,1222,1122,1148]" class="Insecta" family="Pyralidae" genus="Termioptycha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="420" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bilineata">
<emphasis box="[1093,1222,1122,1148]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="420">T. bilineata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[1293,1374,1122,1148]" country="India" name="Sikkim" pageId="5" pageNumber="420">Sikkim</collectingRegion>
is its first time record from 
<collectingCountry box="[400,461,1158,1184]" name="India" pageId="5" pageNumber="420">India</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
